  "text": "In the higgsino decoupling limit for a longitudinal gravitino, the operators from Sec. 4.1 persist after the replacement ζ → G L , and they have the same Wilson coefficients as Eq. (4.5) after removing the tildes from the soft mass parameters. In addition, there are [CITATION_1] We also neglect here possible contributions from interference between diagrams featuring this operator and diagrams in which the fermions originate from an off-shell higgs or Z produced by one of the other dimension 6 operators.",
